  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the newly released Spectral OCT/SLO (OTI, Toronto,
      Canada) with the Zeiss Stratus OCT (Carl-Zeiss Meditec, Dublin, CA) with regards to the
      quality of the images obtained as well as the ease of use.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
